Title: clustered hosts: Fix monitoring if 'Use piggyback data from other hosts if present' is used
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1695036015
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.3.0b1

Clustered hosts with 'No IP', 'No API integrations, no Checkmk agent' and
'Use piggyback data from other hosts if present' options configured, weren't
monitored properly. Clustered services weren't discovered and monitored
even though they were visible in the discovery page.




